# ============================================================
# External LLM Providers (Free Tier) — Distributed Architecture
# ============================================================
# These providers eliminate the need for 230GB+ RAM to run local models.
# Set at least ONE of the following to enable LLM functionality on HF Spaces.

# Groq — Ultra-fast LPU inference (FREE, no credit card)
# Get key: https://console.groq.com/keys
# Free tier: 30 RPM, 14,400 RPD, Llama-3.3-70B, Qwen3-32B
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# Cerebras — Ultra-fast inference (FREE, no credit card)
# Get key: https://cloud.cerebras.ai/
# Free tier: 30 RPM, 1M tokens/day, Llama-3.3-70B
# CEREBRAS_API_KEY=csk_...

# GitHub Models — Free for all GitHub users
# Get token: https://github.com/marketplace/models
# Free tier: 10-15 RPM, 50-150 RPD, GPT-4o, Llama-3.3-70B, DeepSeek-R1
# GITHUB_TOKEN=github_pat_...

# Cloudflare Workers AI — 10K neurons/day free
# Get key: https://dash.cloudflare.com/profile/api-tokens
# CLOUDFLARE_API_KEY=...
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=...

# ============================================================
# GitHub Actions Integration (Research Offloading)
# ============================================================
# Repository to dispatch research jobs to (format: owner/repo)
# GITHUB_REPO=absullh997-rgb/odysseus-original-repo

# ============================================================
# Search APIs (for Deep Research)
# ============================================================
# Serper — Google Search API (free tier: 2,500 queries/month)
# Get key: https://serper.dev/
# SERPER_API_KEY=...

# Tavily — AI-optimized search (free tier: 1,000 queries/month)
# Get key: https://tavily.com/
# TAVILY_API_KEY=...

# Brave Search API (free tier: 2,000 queries/month)
# Get key: https://api.search.brave.com/
# DATA_BRAVE_API_KEY=...
